  <!-- EN: It looks like they want to use sappers to tunnel around your defenses. -->
  <ImmediateAttackSappers.arrivalTextEnemy>看來他們打算派出工兵破解你的防衛。</ImmediateAttackSappers.arrivalTextEnemy>
